#: src/data/org.kde.akonadiimportwizard.desktop:60
msgctxt "Comment"
msgid ""
"Launch the import wizard to migrate data from mailer as thunderbird/"
"evolution etc."
msgstr ""
"मेलरतः thunderbird/evolution इत्यादिरूपेण आँकडानां प्रवासनार्थं आयातविजार्डं प्रारम्भं "
"कुर्वन्तु ।"
